content:
Add the Wrap Up Component to the Chat Transcript Page

To show agents summaries, add the Wrap Up component to the chat transcript page.

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Enterprise and Unlimited Editions with the Einstein for Service add-on

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To create and save Lightning pages in the Lightning App Builder:	Customize Application
From Setup, go to Object Manager.
Select the Case object, and then select Buttons, Links, and Actions.
Either select an existing update record quick action or create one.
To use an existing update a record quick action, add the fields you selected for summary mapping.

From Setup, go to Lightning App Builder.
For the Chat Transcript Record Page, click Edit.
Drag the Einstein Field Recommendations component onto the Chat Transcript Record Page.
Select Wrap Up for the recommendation type, and select your update record quick action for the Update Action.
Click Save and Activate.
title: Adding Wrap Up Component to Service Cloud Chat Transcript Page
